,"
column3: >Metabo ASC Mulit 8 Charger Eight Bay Charger
>Parallel charging means the Metabo 627301000 charges all 8 packs at the SAME TIME. &nbsp
column4: Usually on large capacity chargers like this they charge in sequential format. &nbsp
column5: Sequential charging only charges one pack at a time and then moves on to the next pack. &nbsp
column6: An example of this would be the Milwaukee 48-59-1806 six bay charger. &nbsp
column7: Another example would be with Makita on their two bay versus their four bay charger. &nbsp
column8: The two bay DC18RD charges in sequential order so both are charged at the same time. &nbsp
